+# Part 12.1 — Baby Fork Smoke Project Context Flow
+
+Part 12.1 moves a real minimal context smoke project ahead of generalized Qdrant vector-space work.
+
+## Added
+
+- TaskContext for the baby-fork domain.
+- One stdlib RetrievalWorker stand-in.
+- MVTC producing two variants.
+- ContextGate applying one context patch.
+- Cell Lens journal fed by this real flow.
+- Tests and docs.
+
+## Not added
+
+- No Qdrant dependency.
+- No seven-vector-space implementation.
+- No model dependency.
+- No live system adapter.
+- No command gateway implementation.
